Description: Condition: Excellent with little to no signs of wear! and Nashville star Brad Paisley teamed up to create this incredible limited edition signature Road Worn Telecaster in Silver Sparkle. It features a sandwiched spruce/Paulownia/spruce body with a road worn nitrocellulose lacquer for a unique finish. It features a maple neck with an enhanced "V" neck and oil road worn finish, as well as a maple fingerboard and vintage-style tuners.
